OL,3,C'Sleep disorder has taken over my
OL,4,Clife': Charity warns of a sleep
OL,5,Cpandemic
OL,7,FMichelle Gunter from used to be
OL,8,Fdescribed as "the life and soul of the
OL,9,Fparty".
OL,11,FHowever, due to her sleep disorder the
OL,12,Fmother-of-two was left feeling as if
OL,13,Fher "life was not worth living
OL,14,Fanymore."
OL,16,FIn a heartfelt interview with ITV
OL,17,FWales, Michelle explained how her
OL,18,Finability to sleep has "taken over"
OL,19,Fher whole life.
