OL,3,C'Sleep disorder has taken over my
OL,4,Clife': Charity warns of a sleep
OL,5,Cpandemic
OL,7,FSince then, Michelle's sleep has never
OL,8,Fbeen the same, and is now worse than
OL,9,Fever before.
OL,11,FDespite not sleeping during the day
OL,12,Fand attempting to go to bed early,
OL,13,FMichelle said she wakes up every
OL,14,Ftwenty to forty minutes before finally
OL,15,Fgiving up on sleep altogether,
OL,16,Fbeginning her day at around three in
OL,17,Fthe morning.
OL,19,FShe said: "I'm just losing hope. I
OL,20,Fdon't want to stay like this forever.
OL,21,FI don't like the person I've become.
