OL,3,C'Sleep disorder has taken over my
OL,4,Clife': Charity warns of a sleep
OL,5,Cpandemic
OL,7,FShe said: "The equipment they put on
OL,8,Fyou in unbelievable. You have pipes up
OL,9,Fyour nose all these wires attached to
OL,10,Fyour head, and the environment is a
OL,11,Fhospital ward, it's noisy. It's not a
OL,12,Frelaxing environment."
OL,14,FFour months after her stay at the
OL,15,FSleep Laboratory, Michelle said she
OL,16,Freceived a telephone call diagnosing
OL,17,Fher with mild sleep apnea, periodic
OL,18,Flimb movement disorder and chronic
OL,19,Finsomnia.
