OL,7,FMichelle expressed her frustration
OL,8,Fafter waiting two and a half years for
OL,9,Fa face-to-face consultation.
OL,11,F"Nobody has said 'let's test your
OL,12,Fbloods, let's see if you're
OL,13,Fmenopausal, let's check your iron',
OL,14,Fnothing like that", she said.
