OL,7,FThey also revealed around 14 million
OL,8,Fpeople are currently living with an
OL,9,Fundiagnosed sleep disorder due to the
OL,10,Fnormalisation of disrupted sleep.
OL,12,FLisa Artis said: "There is a sleep
OL,13,Fpandemic and what we mean by that is
OL,14,Fthat there is a sleep crisis and it is
OL,15,Fbecoming a public health issue.
