OL,3,C'Sleep disorder has taken over my
OL,4,Clife': Charity warns of a sleep
OL,5,Cpandemic
OL,7,F"It's having a really serious and
OL,8,Fescalating impact on not only health,
OL,9,Fbut the economy and society as a
OL,10,Fwhole. We know that sleep deprivation
OL,11,Fis linked to a wide range of medical
OL,12,Fissues such as high blood pressure,
OL,13,Ftype two diabetes, heart disease and
OL,14,FAlzheimer's."
OL,16,FThe Sleep Charity's research also
OL,17,Fshowed an average 200,000 working days
OL,18,Fare lost in the UK every year due to
OL,19,Finsufficient sleep, costing the
OL,20,Feconomy up to #40 billion annually.
